{
  "stem": "25773.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then was like a no man's land they created.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then was this new ghetto, started from Leshno street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From Leshno street up to [NON-ENGLISH], up to the absolute north of Warsaw, that was absolutely Jewish part, and that was the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, what they announced is that there will be formed shops.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time what were shops.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "English was not often spoken in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Shops were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Shops.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH], and various other shops in those [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The shops which were formed in the small ghetto, where I was, was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was mainly stitching uniforms for the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the big ghetto, of course, since I was not living there, I wouldn't be able to give an exact account, but my little brother, I secured a place in one big electric, electric-- that was an establishment, a big firm, before the war.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I managed to, to, to register him there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had shoe making, and electricity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And clothes, and brushes for cleaning horses, I believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And boots, hats.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, a big jewelry department, because they robbed Jews of all their--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Whatever belongings they had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, Jewish people in Warsaw left all the pictures, and all the beautiful furniture, and carpets, everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to take fur coats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if it is ever known.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not allowed to take any fur coats or wear any piece of fur on our clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All fur.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Any fur.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bare.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That had to be left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they inherited the fur coats, and they inherited everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
